rong>=E2=80=99s Tod=E2=80=99s Group.) In a statement, a company rep said th=
at Ko, Bagel-Trah, and Touche are all =E2=80=9Cwidely respected global busi=
ness leaders,=E2=80=9D chosen for their =E2=80=9Cmulticultural experience a=
nd other external expertise.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/></p><p style=3D"margin:0;">A=
nyway, it=E2=80=99s no wonder the appointment of three outsiders=E2=80=94in=
cluding one with I.P.O. experience=E2=80=94is fueling questions about wheth=
er the Wertheimers could take Chanel public. This
